HEADWORD: Chronicler
<hw>Chron"i*cler</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A writer of a
chronicle; a recorder of events in the order of time; an
historian.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Such an honest <qex>chronicler</qex> as Griffith.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Chronique</ent>⟦br⟧
